{"id":261145,"type":1,"name":"Astérix le Gaulois","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/1a/35/261145_oLYUR.jpg","summary":"Asterix or The Adventures of Asterix is a series of French comics. The series first appeared in the Franco-Belgian comics magazine Pilote on 29 October 1959. It was written by René Goscinny and illustrated by Albert Uderzo until the death of Goscinny in 1977. Uderzo then took over the writing until 2009, when he sold the rights to publishing company Hachette. In 2013, a new team consisting of Jean-Yves Ferri (script) and Didier Conrad (artwork) took over. As of 2017, 37 volumes have been released. ","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>高卢人阿斯特克斯</li><li><span>册数: </span>37</li><li><span>别名: </span>Asterix</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>高卢英雄历险记</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>The Adventures of Asterix</li><li><span>出版社: </span>Dargaud</li><li><span>发售日: </span>1959-10-29至2010-10-22（旧版）；2009至今（新版）</li>","collection":{"collect":1},"relations":[{"id":261197,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/c9/85/261197_hWKQ0.jpg","title":"Astérix le Gaulois","type":"动画","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/261197"},{"id":113088,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/dc/d7/113088_71Yk2.jpg","title":"Astérix et Cléopâtre","type":"动画","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/113088"},{"id":261198,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/2e/18/261198_MmleU.jpg","title":"Les douze travaux d'Astérix","type":"动画","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/261198"},{"id":261199,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/ed/c6/261199_tyItz.jpg","title":"Astérix et la surprise de César","type":"动画","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/261199"},{"id":261318,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/8d/43/261318_fDd7x.jpg","title":"Astérix chez les Bretons","type":"动画","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/261318"},{"id":117213,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/89/d3/117213_X3XP7.jpg","title":"Astérix et le coup du menhir","type":"动画","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/117213"},{"id":261319,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pi